data.title: Bybit introduces "Ultimate Gold Mine" in year-end treasure hunt event, celebrating a successful 2025.
data.description: In Dubai, UAE on October 31, 2025, Bybit, the second-largest cryptocurrency exchange globally with an impressive trading volume, has excitingly revealed the introduction of the year-end release of the Daily Treasure Hunt called The Ultimate Gold Mine. This initiative is the culmination of Bybit's 2025 reward program, offering participants a chance to win lucrative prizes.

data.title: Twilio (NYSE: TWLO) exceeds Q3 forecasts with revenue of $1.3 billion and $1.25 adjusted earnings per share. Predicts $1.31-$1.32 billion revenue in Q4. CEO Shipchandler highlights strong customer segment growth.
data.description: Twilio Inc (NYSE: TWLO) announced its third-quarter financial results, exceeding expectations. The company reported $1.3 billion in revenue, surpassing analyst projections of $1.25 billion. Additionally, Twilio revealed adjusted earnings of $1.25 per share for the quarter, higher than estimates of $1.08 per share. CEO Khozema Shipchandler expressed satisfaction with the widespread growth in customer segments, from startups to enterprises to ISVs, who continue to select Twilio for their customer engagement needs. Looking ahead to the fourth quarter, Twilio foresees revenue between $1.31 billion to $1.32 billion, compared to expectations of $1.29 billion.
